是全歐洲最大的足球場，入座量高達99,354人。而最近西班牙Jaume Almera地球科學研究所則進行了一項有趣研究。研究人員在距離魯營球場半公里處放置了地震儀，並且留意進行足球比賽時，地震儀的變化。而當每次有巴塞球員射門得分，隨著球迷興奮的上下跳動，引發半公里外的輕微地震，震度數據明顯上升。 而研究數據更指出，今年巴塞隆拿於3月歐洲冠軍聯賽淘汰賽對車路士的比賽中，美斯比賽中入兩球，都成功測到地震波形突然加大。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fd71bca734cc0f66a5868fb473f4759b33765f","tid":633129,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"今年上帝拎梗世界盃懲罰其他國家了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fff6fa89eb844960592b138a77a754119ecd037","tid":633129,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T10:39:18.000Z","msg":"決賽落敗都可以打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小花粉真係智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad95b206ac059f335d591cdd81449ff4e4cd69be","tid":633129,"uid":56589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9fff6fa89eb844960592b138a77a754119ecd037","tid":633129,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T10:39:18.000Z","msg":"決賽落敗都可以打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小花粉真係智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:01:57.000Z","msg":"佢意思係美斯勁過入唔到決賽果d人 例如丙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759929f4151ef7b53133528219ab89e3b70a010c","tid":633129,"uid":171754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:02:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29ae135710e05789b73c280ff3c348aeaef2ab02","tid":633129,"uid":56589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q